item.description: We have liftoff! First attempt at The Grid, a new web dev tool in Beta stage. Reviews of this entirely new idea for a web application have been less than stellar, given all the pre-release hype claiming to transform how we view web pages. By using a "matrix" or Grid, web pages are capable of adjusting color, content layout, and many other visual improvements, based on the content the user provides.
